refer to how spring framework works.

code organization and software stack used.

organized the code in at least three portion:

trading-core: 
	the core of the project. 
	comprises all the specifications/interfaces that must be implemented.
	comprises all the generic services that use the core interfaces 
	and provide additional useful API methods.

[tradestation]-restapi:
	the reference implementation for the specification 

tradingbot-app:
	the main application that uses [Spring] to inject the provider API at runtime. 
	define strategies and can implement app-specific stuff. 
	integration with social media, such as Twitter.


.......
use curl to demonstrate various trading actions like getting a list of instruments, placing an order, or getting historical candlesticks data.



